description:
Thanks for this. I only have one problem, I'm unable to use it with the Emacs snap with racket-mode. I get: system error: Permission denied; errno=13

description: On an older, slower Ubuntu machine, this launches *much* faster than the Flarpack version. (8.9 currently)
